SDMMC002_PasswdType Struct Reference

Detailed Description

This structure contains the Password details. User needs to provide the password information in this structure inorder to use the card's security feature.

uint8_t SDMMC002_PasswdType::NewPassword[SDMMC002_MAX_PASSWD_LEN]

New Password. User needs to set this field at the time of replacing the old password with the new one. Sets to 0 if not replacing the password.
